    / Terms Content
    .bg-white.rounded-lg.shadow-md.p-8.space-y-8

      / Payment Policy
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          2. Payment Policy
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 2.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              Monthly charges are applicable at the start of each service month.
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 2.2.
            %p.text-gray-700
              Wheelsonrent-FZCO reserves the right to terminate this Agreement and suspend services if monthly fees are not received at the beginning of each service month.

      / Cancellation Policy
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          3. Cancellation Policy
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 3.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              The Car Rental Partner reserves the right to cancel the subscription at any time. Monthly payments will cease starting from the subsequent month.
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 3.2.
            %p.text-gray-700
              The Partner shall continue to receive bookings for the current service month. No refunds will be issued for the current month's subscription.

      / Advertising
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          4. Advertising
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 4.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              All promotional content provided by the Partner must comply with Wheelsonrent's advertising guidelines and standards.
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 4.2.
            %p.text-gray-700
              Car rental partners are agreeing that Wheelsonrent show their vehicles on other websites or social media for advertising purpose.

      / Damages and Liability
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          5. Damages and Liability
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 5.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              The Partner is fully responsible for any damages to their vehicles during the rental period.
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 5.2.
            %p.text-gray-700
              The Partner must have appropriate insurance coverage for all vehicles listed on the Wheelsonrent platform.

      / Fines and Penalties
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          6. Fines and Penalties
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 6.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              The Partner shall bear responsibility for any fines or penalties incurred by their vehicles during the rental period.
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 6.2.
            %p.text-gray-700
              The Partner must inform customers of their obligation to cover traffic violations or other penalties incurred during their rental.

      / Termination Policy
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          8. Termination Policy
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 8.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              Either party may terminate this Agreement by providing at least fifteen (15) days' written notice.
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 8.2.
            %p.text-gray-700
              Termination will not affect rentals already booked and confirmed prior to the termination date.

      / Customize Package
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          9. Customize Package
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 9.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              If Car rental partner would like to receive more than 10 monthly bookings (Economy Cars), including Please contact us to customize your package.

      / Terms & Conditions
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          10. Terms & Conditions
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 10.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              If customers extend their rental into the next month, it will be treated as a new booking. Long-term rentals (e.g., 6-month or 1-year) will be counted as three (3) separate bookings.
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 10.2.
            %p.text-gray-700
              If a booking is cancelled due to the vehicle being unavailable without prior notice, it will be considered a Partner-side cancellation and counted as a confirmed booking.
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 10.3.
            %p.text-gray-700
              If a vehicle belongs to two package categories, the higher package shall apply for subscription purpose.

      / Response Time Standards
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          11. Response Time Standards
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 11.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              Car Partners must respond to all customer inquiries within fifteen (15) minutes.
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 11.2.
            %p.text-gray-700
              Failure to do so may result in the booking being reassigned to another Car Rental Partner without notice.

      / Standardized Pricing Policy
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          12. Standardized Pricing Policy
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 12.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              All Car Partners must ensure that vehicles listed on Wheelsonrent are priced at the same or lower rates than those offered on their own platforms or on any other platforms they listed their cars. If prices exceed market rates, Wheelsonrent may suggest adjustments to maintain fair value. To ensure equal opportunity, we aim to keep consistent pricing for similar vehicles, so all partners receive a fair share of customer inquiries.

      / Client Policy and Platform Integrity
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          13. Client Policy and Platform Integrity
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
            %span.flex-shrink-0.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} 13.1.
            %p.text-gray-700
              All Wheelsonrent customers are considered official clients of the platform. Car rental partners are strictly prohibited from redirecting or encouraging these customers to book outside the Wheelsonrent system or bypass the platform in any manner.

      / Vehicle Maintenance & Quality Assurance
      %div
        %h2.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4.pb-2.border-b-2{style: 'color: #3A6363'}
          14. Vehicle Maintenance & Quality Assurance
        .space-y-3.ml-4
          .flex.gap-3
